## Description {#details}

An Iterator for call edges, creates <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/aacalledges">AACallEdges</a> attributes in a lazy way.

This iterator becomes invalid if the underlying edge list changes. So This shouldn&#39;t outlive a iteration of <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/attributor">Attributor</a>.
